:80386,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係安全情況下停車至一旁休息</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個建議適合啲唔夠瞓嘅人 但係我通常都夠瞓 只不過揸車會令人眼瞓 因為我住得太偏 基本上揸親都半粒鐘以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a63828f35aea99e9a17b80c50b815ad1df1fbd","tid":503880,"uid":80386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/183135_88c30edc8662f9f5683f1ff2d316a9b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F183135_88c30edc8662f9f5683f1ff2d316a9b9.jpg&h=95d51f80&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n車都揸唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab5122b2ab10908ba76779d2161370670210503","tid":503880,"uid":40793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"聽歌開大聲啲<br />\n你半個鐘唔算好多呀"},{"pid":"b3a85513ea6158637ec0d47c7f9b5fead0226970","tid":503880,"uid":19738,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係安全情況下停車至一旁休息</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個建議適合啲唔夠瞓嘅人 但係我通常都夠瞓 只不過揸車會令人眼瞓 因為我住得太偏 基本上揸親都半粒鐘以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你搭的士算啦"},{"pid":"9205af800fd69912d51daf9be9447ba260fe6d1f","tid":503880,"uid":40793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"返屋企唔睇下有冇條多灣啲既路楂都楂得專注啲冇咁易眼訓"},{"pid":"94780c8adf9f5ec9984599d09179f46d6f1c2542","tid":503880,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"半個鐘係起跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸多彎嘅路真係唔會眼瞓 不過返歸條路大直路一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開大聲啲歌都試過 不過我架車個喇叭唔靚 開大聲聽會好辛苦 呢個係其中一個比自己換車嘅藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma